<div id="left_content">
<p>
  Sign up now for free!  Just pick a username and password.
  Get quality leads from an experienced yacht brokerage.
  We'll point quality buyers to your yacht.  And advertise
  your yacht on brokerage sites worldwide!
</p>
<p>
  Upgrade to our fee-based account for worldwide listing on 
  YachtAuthority.com.
</p>
<p>
  And upgrade to our classic commision-based account for
  dockage, pricing, magazine advertising, and more!
</p>
</div>

<div id="right_content">
<%= error_messages_for :user %>
<% form_for :user, :url => users_path do |f| -%>
<p><label for="login">Login</label><br/>
<%= f.text_field :login %></p>

<p><label for="email">Email</label><br/>
<%= f.text_field :email %></p>

<p><label for="password">Password</label><br/>
<%= f.password_field :password %></p>

<p><label for="password_confirmation">Confirm Password</label><br/>
<%= f.password_field :password_confirmation %></p>

<p><%= submit_tag 'Sign up' %></p>
<% end -%>
<p><%= link_to '<< Cancel', login_path %></p>
</div>
